# Boundaries

- Keep commercial features (team workspace, SSO, paywalls) out of the OSS kernel.
- Ontology / SPI changes need migration notes or an RFC — do not silently break shapes.
- Dependencies flow: connectors → connector-spi + core; projections → core; cli → packages + connectors.
- Do not add cloud tenancy or multi-tenant assumptions to Personal MVP paths.
- Docs: English is canonical; follow ubiquitous language (Event entity ≠ domain event).
- Commits: Conventional Commits; use `pnpm commit` when unsure.
